PP2A activity status in tissues samples would greatly
simplify biomarker analysis of PP2A function because
it sidesteps the need for analyzing all the possibly rele-
vant subunits. Moreover, as PME-1 inhibits directly
PP2A-C catalytic activity, in addition to regulating its
C-terminal tail methylation [10,14], analysis of PME-1
expression could be a superior diagnostic method over
